<Base title="SocialProof for Pet Boarding Facilities — Client Testimonials That Win Trust | SocialProof" description="Pet boarding facilities and kennels: collect and display client testimonials to win more bookings and reassure anxious pet owners that their fur babies are in good hands.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">Social Proof for Pet Boarding Facilities</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">Leaving their pet behind is stressful for every owner. They're not just comparing prices — they're searching for proof that someone will care for their dog or cat as lovingly as they would. Real testimonials from fellow pet owners are the most powerful trust signal you can show a nervous prospect.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Reassure anxious pet owners before they book</h2>
      <p>The decision to board a pet is emotionally charged. Your facility photos and amenity list help — but what tips the scale is reading that another pet owner's dog "was excited to come back" or "got more attention than we expected." SocialProof makes it easy to collect and display those reassuring stories on your website.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What pet owners say that converts bookings</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
