        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "Sent photo updates twice a day without being asked. Made our vacation so much more relaxing."</li>
        <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> "Followed all our special instructions perfectly — dietary needs, medication, sleep schedule. All of it."</li>
        <li><strong>Facility:</strong> "Clean, spacious, and smelled fresh even in the kennel area. Impressed."</li>
        <li><strong>Repeat business:</strong> "Our dog literally pulls us toward the door when we pull into the parking lot. She loves it there."</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for boarding facilities</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your homepage and booking page.</li>
        <li><strong>Email or text the collection link</strong> when owners pick up their pet.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve each testimonial</strong> before it appears.</li>
        <li><strong>Watch new pet owners choose you with confidence</strong> because they've read real stories.</li>
      </ol>
